725763f-a.title: Queens: 101st Avenue - 103rd Street
725763f-a.text:
101st Avenue, at the S.W. corner of 103rd Street, showing
the St. Marys Ronan Catholic Church. The view is westward frowa
105th Street and shows also the rectory on the corner of 104th
Street. The 3-story building on the left is also church property.
P. L. Sperr  June 6, 1927
NO REERODUCTIONS
